social_posts.post_text: While we were on our first family trip in Montana @jeremiahandrachel captured our first official family photos and to say I’m in love is an understatement. ❤️ Time goes way too fast. I swear in just a few weeks Luca already looks different. Emotional Mama over here.
A few film shots from our time in the Amalfi Coast. I hardly share personal work, but I’ve enjoyed sharing something different lately. Here’s a snippet of the gorgeous views. ✨

Our website is slowly but surely getting updated! Feeling grateful and emotional about all of the events and people I photographed over the years. Thank you to everyone who has supported me through all the different seasons of life and business. 💓

This week Brian and I celebrated our two year anniversary! It's so hard to believe that another year has passed so quickly. 

I am so proud of us for the past two years. Becoming parents together had challenges and now we have both grown and changed together. 

As always, life is full of so much joy and adventure with my guy. Today I’m just filled with gratitude for all the moments I’ve had the chance to share with him, both big and small.

Taking some time to reflect on my journey as a wedding photographer. From capturing intimate moments between couples over the years to documenting their big day, I'm beyond grateful. 

Moving forward, I want to push myself creatively and experiment with new techniques to deliver even better photos for my clients. I have big dreams for the future.  I'm so excited about what's to come and I'm determined to make those dreams a reality.

Thank you to all of my clients and followers for your support. I couldn't have come this far without you. Here's to the next chapter!

You may not know that your wedding venue holds the key to capturing those magical moments and stunning photos. ✨

The venue sets the stage, adding depth and character to your images. The venues lighting plays a vital role, transforming ordinary moments into extraordinary ones. Your venue colors set the mood, infusing warmth and personality into your photos. Choose your venue wisely, as it becomes a canvas for your love story and the perfect setting for capturing cherished memories. 
_____ 
For my fellow photographers: One of our favorite Virginia venues, @pippinhillfarm, photographed on Portra 400 developed by our lab @photovisionprints

One of the most essential pieces to grabbing creative shots? Trust your photographer's vision and give them time to get creative. 

We were capturing portraits and we were taking a short break while I was changing out my film roll when I got the inspiration for this very shot! 

They were looking at one another, and as he quickly turned to look out at the snow in appreciation and she glanced and me and was totally inspired to recapture my observation from moments before.

The moment of pause is what inspired this photograph and we don’t often consider how beneficial small moments of cushion time can be for creativity. 

By letting us do our thing and allowing for some creative freedom and time, we can bring out the unique beauty of your love story with our full creativity. 

Give us the time to explore and experiment, and we'll find the perfect lighting, angles, and compositions ✨

I had such a blast capturing this beautiful celebration at the beautiful @great.marsh ✨

For my fellow photographers, Portra 400 scanned by @photovisionprints

Tips for visiting the Amalfi Coast in August! 🇮🇹❤️

✨ Sorrento: Make Sorrento your home-base for its charm, vibrancy, and awe-inspiring vistas. From here, easily arrange a boat tour along the Amalfi Coastline and to Capri!

✨Set Sail and Explore: Take a boat tour from Sorrento to witness the stunning Amalfi Coastline and Capri. Spend one day exploring the coast and another in Capri, immersing yourself in gorgeous landscapes, swimming, and making memories with friends from around the world!

Iconic Towns to Discover:

Hidden Gems of Positano: Stroll through narrow streets, embrace vibrant culture, and savor panoramic views from cliffside vantage points.

Amalfi’s Timeless Charm: Wander picturesque streets, marvel at ancient architecture, and soak in the stunning coastal backdrop.

Ravello’s Enchanting Heights: Ascend to the mountaintop village of Ravello, where breathtaking vistas, lush gardens, and a romantic atmosphere await.

Save this post for your future adventure! ✨

I've had the incredible opportunity to explore stunning landscapes all around the world.

I've come to realize that beauty isn't just reserved for those far-off destinations. It's hiding in every little moment and every corner of our own backyards. 

The real magic happens in the everyday scenes, the simple moments. ✨
Luxurious details that elevate your overall bridal look, making you feel like a true vision of elegance and sophistication. ✨

Becoming a mother has gifted me with a new lens, one that magnifies the fleeting moments.

I can't help but reflect on my own journey as a mother, the moments of tenderness, and the pure joy of witnessing my child's milestones. 🤍

Warmest congratulations to the newlyweds! It was an absolute honor to document every moment at the stunning @dover_hall with a dream team. Wishing you both a lifetime of cherished memories and happiness! 🤍
